{"type":null,"faqId":44666,"title":"忘记了屏幕解锁密码或图案","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.24791667in;margin-left:0.95694447in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.24791667in;margin-left:0.95694447in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:0.93958336in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p8{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p9{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.29652777in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>设置图案解锁时，请根据屏幕提示设置备用数字密码。忘记解锁图案时，可以通过备用数字密码解锁屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若忘记了备用解锁密码，可以通过升级手机的方法解决。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160189\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>升级后，手机内部存储中的数据将被删除。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请根据手机的支持情况选择一种升级方式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n <span>通过 microSD 卡升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span>华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span>，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>将升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入 microSD 卡根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>在关机状态下，插入 microSD 卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>手机进入升级模式开始升级，升级完成后手机将恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>通过外接存储设备升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span>华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span>，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>将升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入 U 盘根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>在关机状态下，使用 USB OTG 数据线连接手机和 U 盘。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标，手机自动进入升级模式开始升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=160190\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p9\">\n<span>请使用华为认可的 USB OTG 数据线，如需购买，请访问华为商城或联系供应商。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>升级完成后手机将恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若无法升级，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"167","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409018000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":145,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"屏幕解锁,密码,忘记,图案","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}